WEBVTT

00:12:59.154 --> 00:13:00.154
[to = ljubav]

00:13:00.154 --> 00:13:03.011
Suze koje se liju liju se zbog toga.

00:13:03.035 --> 00:13:05.520
Ljudi koji su to osjetili, ne lažu o tome.

00:13:05.544 --> 00:13:07.932
Živjeti bez toga, bili biste izgubljeni.

00:13:07.956 --> 00:13:10.194
Kad sam u tome i osjećam to,
vičem o tome.

00:13:10.194 --> 00:13:12.318
Svi na svijetu znaju za to.

00:13:12.318 --> 00:13:14.166
Ranjen sam i slomljen
i plovim oko toga,

00:13:14.166 --> 00:13:16.612
radim to krivo,
jer to nisam dozvolio.

00:13:16.612 --> 00:13:19.054
Zarasta li rana i ožiljak bez toga?

00:13:19.078 --> 00:13:21.923
Može li se osjećaj toga sakriti?

00:13:21.947 --> 00:13:24.935
Svi imaju svoj ideal toga,

00:13:24.959 --> 00:13:26.402
sanjaju o tome,

00:13:26.426 --> 00:13:27.816
apel za to.

00:13:28.382 --> 00:13:30.298
Pa, što je to u tome?